 <sect2 xml:id="sec.power.requirements.sw">
  <title>Software Requirements</title>
  <para>
   A Web browser able to connect to &powerkvm; running on the &powerlinux;
   server is required. With this Web browser you will perform pre-installation
   steps using the Kimchi Web interface.
  </para>
 </sect2>
